{"tid":1743518,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［協助義士］與其叫勝選議員捐錢，不如叫佢地請啲因爲被捕而失業嘅手足","createTime":"2019-11-21T08:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T13:23:58.000Z","uid":134794,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17dd78a8aa7a6c837ab7917214de418751f8e6fb","tid":1743518,"uid":134794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"區議員大概一個月有$46000實報實銷開支津貼<br />\n其實一個盡責嘅區議員係值$30000人工，與其好似威脅候選人捐錢，倒不如優先請一啲因爲被補而失業嘅手足<br />\n好多手足都有骨氣，唔要施捨，而且手足係需要一份工作多於金錢補償，長時間失業會影響手足第時搵工<br />\n但政府一定唔會請佢地，私人公司好多都唔會請<br />\n如果辦事處需要請人，而手足能力條件符合要求<br />\n可唔可以優先聘用<br />\n<br />\n贊成嘅請幫手推 或者 將建議交俾候選人"},{"pid":"c7337274bfe015048b89c9945e0c55ffe86e6106","tid":1743518,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U84oZn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU84oZn6.jpg&h=065a56a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMbyB1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMbyB1k.jpg&h=604a5751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期五夜晚，各區商場和理非唱歌，區選前最大型和理非行動，想問下你會唔會參與？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"10c356cff1bc42afe7f7ca4e4dd254df55a80ecf","tid":1743518,"uid":134794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"697d43f58959c69a83b8092bfb4f5c1ebe0ff8aa","tid":1743518,"uid":134794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:47:48.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"df3d65056980237cf71cb26eb8d005fcd654fa29","tid":1743518,"uid":134794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"1e61c76af43fd10fb2b1aa064c6ee1cf6d2c3f5e","tid":1743518,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5c6469368b